Remove:

```java
@InjectMocks
private PartnerRepositoryClient partnerRepositoryClient;
```

The constructor order must match the fields in your production class. Based on your class, it is probably:

```java
public PartnerRepositoryClient(
        WebClient webClient,
        RestClient partnerRepoClient
)
```

If IntelliJ reports a different constructor, use the exact order it suggests.

